<h1>Breakpoints</h1>

<p class="warning-note">
	<strong>NOTICE</strong>: The goal is to use those breakpoints in all our products. Please replace the old breakpoints with the new ones whenever and wherever possible.
</p>

<p>
	Support for multiple breakpoints is vital for proper display of content across various browser sizes.
	While historically our main audience has come through on desktop, mobile viewing of Fandom's content has surpassed
	desktop traffic. Breakpoints allow for the proper display of content and advertising across devices.
	Design and engineering should create with responsiveness in mind, planning for multiple breakpoints.
</p>
<p class="alert-info">
	{{wds-icon name='alert' class='wds-icon-small'}}
	If you want to see documentation on outdated breakpoints check {{#link-to 'base-styles.breakpoints'}}here{{/link-to}}.
</p>

