<section>
	<h2 id="mixins">Useful mixns</h2>
	<p>
		It's recommended to use the following mixins to make implementation easier.
	</p>
	<h3>Content well mixin</h3>
	<p>
		In order to get proper margins automatically on any breakpoint one can use <code class="format-code">wds-content-well</code> mixin in the code.
	</p>
	<h3>Hide on breakpoints mixin</h3>
	<p>
		If there's a need to hide particular element on some of the breakpoints the <code class="format-code">wds-hide-on-breakpoint(<em>breakpoint</em>)</code> mixin should be used.<br/>
		The breakpoint (or list of breakpoints) is passed in the param.
	</p>
	<h3>Examples:</h3>
	{{#code-sample language='scss'}}
.content {
	@include wds-content-well;

	.extra-content {
		@include wds-hide-on-breakpoint(small)
	}

	.content-only-on-mobile {
		@include wds-hide-on-breakpoint(medium-up);
	}

	.content-only-on-medium-and-large {
		@include wds-hide-on-breakpoint(small xlarge-up);
	}
}
	{{/code-sample}}
</section>

